'''Kuroba mu buryo butemewe mu [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|kiyaga cya Kivu]]''' ni ibikorwa bitemewe byo gukura amoko atandukanye y’amafi ku mpamvu zitandukanye mu [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|kiyaga cya Kivu]] . Ibikorwa byo kuroba bihungabanya urusobe rw’ibinyabuzima byo mu mazi, niyo mpamvu leta yashyizeho amategeko agenga uburobyi. Abantu baturiye ikiyaga barashobora kuroba mu buryo butemewe kugirango bongere amafaranga kandi babone uburyo bwo kubaho ariko kurundi ruhande ibyo bigira ingaruka kubicuruzwa rusange by'amafi aturutse mu [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|kiyaga cya Kivu]] . <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/section/read/72514</ref> Uburobyi butemewe muri [[Afurika]] ni imwe mu mpamvu nyamukuru zitera uburobyi kuko leta y'[[Rwanda|u Rwanda]] rimwe na rimwe ihagarika ibikorwa by’uburobyi mu [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|kiyaga cya Kivu]] mu gihe kizwi nka 'biology break', <ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/202110070045.html</ref> kandi kuroba cyane ni indi mpamvu itera indwara mu mafi. <ref>https://academic.oup.com/crawlprevention/governor?content=%2fcid%2farticle-lookup%2fdoi%2f10.1093%2fcid%2fcit559</ref>

== Ibisobanuro ==
Muri 2018, hagaragaye ibibazo birenga 400 by’uburobyi butemewe n'amategeko ku [[Ikiyaga cya Kivu|kiyaga cya Kivu]] kandi kubera uburobyi butemewe bushingiye ku gukoresha ibikoresho byangiza, umusaruro w’amafi mu kiyaga cya Kivu wavuye kuri toni 24 199 muri 2017 ugera kuri toni 16 194 muri 2020 nicyo igipimo kinini cya 28% mu gihombo niko minisiteri y'Ubuhinzi n’Ubworozi biganisha ku Iterambere ry’Umutungo kamere yavuze. Hagati ya Gicurasi na Nyakanga 2020, ibiro bya polisi ishinzwe umutekano mu mazi mu [[Rwanda]] byatangaje ibirego 27 birimo 10 ba rushimusi batawe muri yombi bazira kuroba mu buryo butemewe. <ref>https://enactafrica.org/enact-observer/tipping-the-scales-of-illicit-fishing-in-lake-kivu</ref> <ref>https://issafrica.org/iss-today/tipping-the-scales-of-illicit-fishing-in-lake-kivu</ref>

